DAILY COMMANDS

Open terminal in correct folder
File Explorer > fnf-agents folder
Click address bar > type: powershell > Enter


Research Agent
python run_agents.py --agent research --topic "your topic"


WordPress Agent — create draft
python run_agents.py --agent wordpress


Check post status and IDs
python check_posts.py


Publish a draft post (replace 291 and title)
python -c "from agent_3_wordpress import WordPressAgent; a = WordPressAgent(); print(a._publish_wp_post(291, 'Title Here'))"


Full pipeline (all 3 agents)
python run_agents.py --all --topic "your topic"



