SECURITY RULES

Never commit .env to GitHub
Never share API keys in chat or email
Use Application Password for WordPress — not login password
Always review draft before publishing
Agent never publishes without YES confirmation

WORDPRESS SETTINGS

Permalinks: Post name (Settings > Permalinks)
REST API test: funnynfunny.com/wp-json/wp/v2/posts
If REST API returns HTML: fix permalinks (SOAP-004)


